The '''Gachoogai River''' was located on [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]], between [[Peace City|Colony One]] and [[Colony Two]]. [[Muuurgh]] had to navigate its fast currents to reach Colony Two during his search for [[Mrrov]].

